'''Mavrille Street''' was one of the few streets in the [[Calius saj Leeloo]] that had been carved wide enough for vehicular travel. It was also a direct route from the Tower in which [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn's]] clone army was housed to the Calius landing field. The street marked the location where [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Talon Karrde]] began to track the possible sources of Thrawn's clones.

